Description:
    Generate api

Example:
    rails generate hatio_resource_api Product id:string domain_id:string name:string --bundle=comp --id_type=uuid

    This will create:
    	app/controllers/products_controller.rb
		app/models/products.rb
		db/migrate/20121010120000_create_products.rb
		app/views/products/index.json.jbuilder
		app/views/products/show.json.jbuilder
		app/views/products/create.json.jbuilder
		app/views/products/update.json.jbuilder
		app/views/products/destroy.json.jbuilder
